ct) {\n\n                // handles both nulls\n                return i;\n            }\n\n            if (object != null && object.equals(array[i])) {\n                return i;\n            }\n        }\n\n        return -1;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     *  Basic find for small arrays of int.\n     */\n    public static int find(int[] array, int value) {\n\n        for (int i = 0; i < array.length; i++) {\n            if (array[i] == value) {\n\n[1524 more lines in file. Use offset=261 to continue.]"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1779524474299}}
